{"tid":1511764,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"各位想搞狗仔狗女入一入黎","createTime":"2019-08-27T15:36:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T16:06:01.000Z","uid":174065,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f853d6f2d31297dc97c91cd3da9f44d9617e827e","tid":1511764,"uid":174065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:36:19.000Z","msg":"首先, 我認為唔同狗仔女講野只係會令佢地更仇恨示威者, 反而令到佢嘅犬父更加針對示威者。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而係咁講黑警壞話會令到佢地無地自容, 想埋堆但係又唔埋得, 仲要係佢地自己孤立自己。跟住再係咁洗佢地腦，令到佢地都唔信自己老豆老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再翻屋企面對犬父母, 繼而就會鬧交, 令到狗仔女都企埋我地呢邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完全無欺凌成份, 幾乖嘅學生都做得, 佢地賴都無得賴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我建議全日都講黑警, 講到佢地羞恥為止, 洗埋佢地腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"438f798ec9e0c6c6477dba0c12e48217e8493ca8","tid":1511764,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce1d0cc9e175335b0fa896c7ef996d190ef4f882","tid":1511764,"uid":154892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:37:13.000Z","msg":"認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔洗出手既 策反佢地更重要"},{"pid":"469556f5501291687831be46de8d87728ddf92d2","tid":1511764,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:40:21.000Z","msg":"撐我哋嘅就係自己人<br />\n否則當佢撐驚, 要大大力欺凌佢哋"},{"pid":"7f6a0126ac4a69863c26f072a6519e045511fa09","tid":1511764,"uid":174065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:44:39.000Z","msg":"不過無論點 核彈都唔割！ 只係比多個選擇大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b45fee0463767227474eac8cf7d042f5a1ef04f","tid":1511764,"u